interpretation:
The "outbox tray" emoji represents the act of sending something out into the world, whether it be a message, a project, or an idea. This card suggests that you are ready to take action and share your creations with others. It can also indicate a need to let go of something that is no longer serving you, and to release it out into the universe. 

In a reading, the "outbox tray" can signify the successful completion of a project or the need to take action and send a message or proposal. It can also represent the end of a chapter in your life and the importance of letting go and moving forward. This card encourages you to trust in the universe and have faith that your efforts will be received positively.
